These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-1::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  engineer, police-officer, dancer, journalist
4 different games are played: monopoly, billiard, scrabble, go
1. the person playing monopoly is somewhere to the left of the person playing scrabble##5
2. the police-officer is not the person playing monopoly##6
3. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the person playing go##1
4. the dancer is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1
5. the engineer is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
6. the person playing monopoly is not the dancer##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |    2     |    3     |    4    |
| Beverage   | police-officer   | journalist    | engineer    | dancer |
| Sport      | go | monopoly | scrabble | billiard |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-2::.
City: san-francisco, hannover, paris, boston
The people use 4 different means of transport: ship, subway, bus, train
1. the person driving the ship is on the far right##1
2. the person traveling to hannover is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to paris##5
3. the person driving the train is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to boston##5
4. the person traveling to hannover is not the person driving the subway##6
5. the person driving the train is on the left of the person traveling to paris##1
6. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
7. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
8. the person traveling to paris is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| Beverage   | hannover  | paris    | san-francisco | boston    |
| Food       | train | subway | bus  | ship |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-3::.
There 4 different types of food: mango, carrot, kiwi, lemon
The people use 4 different means of transport: snowmobile, subway, motorbike, jet-ski
1. the person eating lemon is not the person driving the snowmobile##6
2. the person driving the subway is not the person eating kiwi##6
3. the person driving the motorbike is on the left or right of the person eating carrot##3
4. the person driving the subway is the person eating mango##1
5. the person eating carrot is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
6. the person eating mango is in an odd position##4
7. the person driving the snowmobile is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person driving the motorbike is somewhere to the left of the person driving the jet-ski##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |       2        |   3    |   4    |
| Beverage   | lemon       | carrot  | mango  | kiwi |
| Job        | motorbike | jet-ski | subway | snowmobile  |

