.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-4::.
House: townhouse, colonial, tower, wooden
4 different games are played: scrabble, snooker, domino, billiard
1. the tower house is on the left of the wooden house##1
2. the colonial house is somewhere to the left of the person playing scrabble##5
3. the person playing billiard is not the colonial house##6
4. the person playing billiard is somewhere to the right of the person playing scrabble##5
5. the person playing domino is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
6. the wooden house is somewhere to the left of the person playing billiard##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |     3     |    4     |
| Pet         | colonial | tower | wooden     | townhouse |
| Transport   | snooker     | domino    | scrabble | billiard    |

