.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-5::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  manager, librarian, software-developer, police-officer
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: january, june, december, march
1. the manager is on the left of the police-officer##1
2. the police-officer is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in december##5
3. the police-officer is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in june##5
4. the librarian is not the person who's birthday is in march##6
5. the person who's birthday is in january is not the manager##6
6. the software-developer is on the left of the librarian##1
7. the person who's birthday is in december is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |  2   |    3     |   4   |
| Beverage    | manager        | police-officer | software-developer | librarian |
| Transport   | march | january | june     | december   |

