.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-6::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: hip-hop, electronic, punk, trance
House: tower, cottage, modern, wooden
1. the tower house is on the right of the fan hip-hop##1
2. the fan trance is not the cottage house##6
3. the tower house is on the far right##1
4. the cottage house is somewhere to the right of the wooden house##5
5. the fan punk is the fan punk##1
6. the fan punk is somewhere to the left of the tower house##5
7. the fan punk is somewhere to the left of the fan hip-hop##5
8. the fan electronic is somewhere to the left of the wooden house##5
9. the fan electronic is somewhere to the left of the wooden house##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |     3     |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | electronic | punk    | hip-hop  | trance   |
| Nationality   | modern  | wooden | cottage | tower |

