.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-7::.
4 different games are played: scrabble, mah-jongg, monopoly, backgammon
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: bellflower, sunflower, aconite, daisy
1. the person who growsaconite is on the left or right of the person who growsbellflower##3
2. the person who growsaconite is not the person playing mah-jongg##6
3. the person playing scrabble is the person who growssunflower##1
4. the person who growsbellflower is on the left or right of the person who growsdaisy##3
5. the person who growsaconite is on the far left##1
6. the person playing mah-jongg is the person who growsbellflower##1
7. the person playing backgammon is somewhere to the left of the person who growsbellflower##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |      3      |      4      |
| Movie-Genre   | backgammon | mah-jongg     | monopoly | scrabble |
| Music-Genre   | aconite | bellflower | daisy      | sunflower         |

