2. the person playing mah-jongg is somewhere to the left of the person playing scrabble##5
3. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
4. the person playing bridge is on the left or right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##3
5. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left or right of the person playing bridge##3
6. the person playing chess is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rowing##3
7. the person who's sport is soccer is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is baseball##5
8. the person who's sport is lacrosse is not the person playing mah-jongg##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |     2      |       3       |      4       |
| Beverage   | lacrosse  | rowing        | baseball      | soccer          |
| Job        | chess | bridge | mah-jongg | scrabble |

