.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-10::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, swisher, tiparillo, alhambra
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: comedy, sports, mystery, horror
1. the person watching comedy movies is not the old-henry-smoker##6
2. the alhambra-smoker is on the left of the swisher-smoker##1
3. the person watching horror movies is the person watching horror movies##1
4. the alhambra-smoker is on the right of the person watching horror movies##1
5. the tiparillo-smoker is not the person watching horror movies##6
6. the person watching sports movies is not the swisher-smoker##6
7. the person watching horror movies is in an even position##4
8. the tiparillo-smoker is the person watching comedy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |       2       |    3    |    4     |
| Pet     | tiparillo | old-henry        | alhambra  | swisher     |
| Sport   | comedy     | horror | sports | mystery |

