.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-11::.
4 different pets are kept: ferret, fish, pony, snake
There 4 different types of food: potato, banana, asparagus, watermelon
1. the owner of the ferret is on the left or right of the owner of the snake##3
2. the person eating banana is somewhere to the left of the owner of the ferret##5
3. the person eating asparagus is not the owner of the pony##6
4. the owner of the fish is between the person eating watermelon and the owner of the pony##2
5. the owner of the pony is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
6. the person eating banana is between the person eating potato and the owner of the ferret##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |   3   |     4     |
| Hobby         | pony | fish    | ferret | snake |
| Music-Genre   | potato         | banana | watermelon   | asparagus     |

