3. the person who growsazalea is the person who likes fuchsia##1
4. the person who growsazalea is on the right of the person who likes white##1
5. the person who growszinnia is not the person who likes fuchsia##6
6. the person who likes white is not the person who growsmarigold##6
7. the person who likes orange is somewhere to the left of the person who likes white##5
8. the person who likes lilac is on the left of the person who likes orange##1

.:: Answer ::.
