2. the person drinking water is not the owner of the snake##6
3. the person drinking coffee is the owner of the ferret##1
4. the person drinking soy-milk is somewhere to the right of the owner of the snake##5
5. the person drinking coffee is between the person drinking water and the owner of the frog##2
6. the person drinking water is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Food          | almond-milk | water      | coffee | soy-milk   |
| Movie-Genre   | snake     | guinea-pig | ferret   | frog |

