1. the person playing mah-jongg is somewhere to the right of the person playing bridge##5
2. the person playing canasta is somewhere to the right of the person playing mah-jongg##5
3. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
4. the person playing scrabble is not the prince-smoker##6
5. the swisher-smoker is between the prince-smoker and the chaman-smoker##2
6. the game-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
7. the game-smoker is on the right of the prince-smoker##1
8. the person playing scrabble is somewhere to the right of the person playing mah-jongg##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2     |      3      |      4      |
| Hobby   | chaman | swisher | prince | game |
| Pet     | bridge  | mah-jongg      | canasta  | scrabble       |

