.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-20::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: green, chestnut, mauve, aquamarine
The people have 4 different hobbies: writing, card-games, skydiving, magic-tricks
1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left or right of the person who likes chestnut##3
2. the person who likes aquamarine is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is card-games##3
3. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
4. the person who's hobby is writing is not the person who likes green##6
5. the person who likes aquamarine is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##5
6. the person who's hobby is card-games is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |    2     |     3      |     4     |
| Beverage    | green | chestnut | aquamarine      | mauve   |
| Transport   | magic-tricks  | card-games   | skydiving | writing |

 